        <h2 class="page-headings">Meet our students</h2>
        
<div class="row card-set">
    <div class="col">
        <div class="card-set-grid">



<div class="card-container">
    <img class="card-image w-100" src="//ctfimages.intoglobal.com/xw2h6mjophtz/7JuMV3J8lgeR1CStOTB349/02ff161246bfea317e00b0bde1f72229/Hugo-card.jpg" alt="Hugo, a Business Student" />
    <div class="card-content">
        
        <h4 class="card-heading">Gain crucial industry experience</h4>
        <p class="card-copy">
            Business graduate Hugo kick-started his career thanks to 
a work placement during his degree at Exeter.
